$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
is_citizen_of

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
is_citizen_of -  This method checks to see if the specified person is a citizen or not.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int is_citizen_of(string area,
string citizen)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^area%^RESET%^ - the area to check them in
%^BOLD%^citizen%^RESET%^ - the person to check for citizenship
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 if they are a citizen, 0 if not

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/inherit/citizens.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method checks to see if the specified person is a citizen or
not.
.EP

